Subject: Secunia Research: Autonomy KeyView wkssr.dll
	Floating Point Conversion Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 28/07/2010

                    - Autonomy KeyView wkssr.dll - 
            - Floating Point Conversion Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

